title: Personal collection of Arabic, Kurdish and Farsi music
description:
An incredible collection of music by Arabic, Kurdish and Persian artists. This is a personal collection from my computer, it contains only the best of the best. I have lived most of my life in the Kurdistan parts of Iran and Iraq and I know *something* about good Eastern music.

Most of the files have proper ID3 tags, so don't worry about the file names.

PS: I am sending these files to a friend and using TPB as the tracker. I guarantee that the music files work. But please kindly do not download the books and the diaries.
